text._text: Here for you. There for you.

image._alt: Shot or rear portion of Altra Paradigm 6, showing the Ego Max sole.

customhtml2_copy_cop_229667436._customHTML:
SUPPORT WHEN YOU NEED IT

Our GuideRail™ technology encourages natural foot placement and provides added medial guidance—but only when it’s needed.

customhtml2_copy._customHTML:
WITH YOU EVERY STRIDE
Our Altra EGO™ midsole offers a soft yet responsive ride, added flexibility, and underfoot feel.

customhtml2_copy_cop_229667436._customHTML:
GET LOCKED IN

The updated molded heel cup is integrated into the collar and is designed to provide a more secure, locked-in feel.

customhtml2._customHTML:
COMFORT YOU CAN COUNT ON

Our signature FootShape™ comfort gives your feet more space to sit naturally and is designed to address biological differences in men's and women's feet.

image._alt: Side-by-side image of Women's and Men's Altra Provision 6

content._jcr:description: The Altra Provision 6 gives you support when you need it, for a smooth and comfortable road run. Altra EGO™ midsole foam gives the added flexibility you need.
